{"id": "1446916344590241863", "channel_id": "1446916344590241863", "type": 0, "author_id": "724610866678595615", "author_name": "soleil_sun", "author_bot": false, "content": "達芙戴爾路過後，拉蒙娜提醒詹金的對話前後文有衝突\n最近在重看劇情，希望我不會太頻繁出現在這裡 <:Clown:1400771541423226971>\n\n喔，還有從開服至今圖魯的自稱有時候「余」有時候「餘」的問題\n（圖片下補）\n實際上在繁中裡用於自稱的只會是「余」\n只有在用來表示「剩下、多餘」時，它們才會是通同字\n\n「发」寫在繁中有「髮（三聲）」和「發（一聲）」兩個字\n薩爾瓦多這邊應該為「生發」\n（圖片下補）\n且兩字並不存在能通同的用法", "timestamp": "2025-12-06T17:28:58.956000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-06T17:51:15.493000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1446916344967594024", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 612105, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1446916344590241863/1446916344967594024/image.png?ex=6a00c05b&is=69ff6edb&hm=505ba4d4afc78751c226813db81f96f7dae8cea98927d7b98b205b162c8a8aac&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1446916344590241863", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「处理中」2-2【三條規則】前後文衝突、其他文案繁體化有誤（錯字）", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1446806809074602066", "channel_id": "1446806809074602066", "type": 0, "author_id": "984914637126516767", "author_name": "serialexperimentsmid", "author_bot": false, "content": "The existing official art is nice but I find it kind of hard to reference when trying to draw Fan Art, especially since you can't really deviate from the standard outfits if the character is unique like Castor or Faros.  Given how diverse the bodies are in this game it would be nice to be able to create outfits for characters accurately. For example it would be amazing if Ryker's fur pattern was specified so that people could draw him in casual or summer clothing accurately.", "timestamp": "2025-12-06T10:13:43.654000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1446806809074602066", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Will official character design reference sheets of Awakeners and Characters be created?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
